name: Kawasaki Ninja H2R™
description: The Kawasaki Ninja H2R™ is a closed course riding use only model and is not manufactured for use on public roads, streets or highways. The "supercharged supersport" class motorcycle was manufactured by Kawasaki™ Heavy Industries and features a variable-speed centrifugal-type supercharger. With a claimed 300 horsepower (220 kW), it has 50% more power than the fastest street-legal motorcycles.
